Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.17,0:22:13.26,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我许下这样的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:16.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}跨越悲伤的壁垒
