Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.49,0:23:01.64,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我许下这样的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.64,0:23:04.96,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}仿佛那冲破黑暗的
